21static inline isc_result_t
22fromtext_sink(ARGS_FROMTEXT) {
23 isc_token_t token;
24
25 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_sink);
26
27 UNUSED(type);
28 UNUSED(rdclass);
29 UNUSED(origin);
30 UNUSED(options);
31 UNUSED(callbacks);
32
33 /* meaning */
34 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token, isc_tokentype_number,
35 false));
36 if (token.value.as_ulong > 0xffU)
37 RETTOK(ISC_R_RANGE);
38 RETERR(uint8_tobuffer(token.value.as_ulong, target));
39
40 /* coding */
41 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token, isc_tokentype_number,
42 false));
43 if (token.value.as_ulong > 0xffU)
44 RETTOK(ISC_R_RANGE);
45 RETERR(uint8_tobuffer(token.value.as_ulong, target));
46
47 /* subcoding */
48 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token, isc_tokentype_number,
49 false));
50 if (token.value.as_ulong > 0xffU)
51 RETTOK(ISC_R_RANGE);
52 RETERR(uint8_tobuffer(token.value.as_ulong, target));
53
54 return(isc_base64_tobuffer(lexer, target, -1));
55}
56
57static inline isc_result_t
58totext_sink(ARGS_TOTEXT) {
59 isc_region_t sr;
60 char buf[sizeof("255 255 255")];
61 uint8_t meaning, coding, subcoding;
62
63 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_sink);
64 REQUIRE(rdata->length >= 3);
65
66 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &sr);
67
68 /* Meaning, Coding and Subcoding */
69 meaning = uint8_fromregion(&sr);
70 isc_region_consume(&sr, 1);
71 coding = uint8_fromregion(&sr);
72 isc_region_consume(&sr, 1);
73 subcoding = uint8_fromregion(&sr);
74 isc_region_consume(&sr, 1);
75 snprintf(buf, sizeof(buf), "%u %u %u", meaning, coding, subcoding);
76 RETERR(str_totext(buf, target));
77
78 if (sr.length == 0U)
79 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
80
81 /* data */
82 if ((tctx->flags & DNS_STYLEFLAG_MULTILINE) != 0)
83 RETERR(str_totext(" (", target));
84
85 RETERR(str_totext(tctx->linebreak, target));
86
87 if (tctx->width == 0) /* No splitting */
88 RETERR(isc_base64_totext(&sr, 60, "", target));
89 else
90 RETERR(isc_base64_totext(&sr, tctx->width - 2,
91 tctx->linebreak, target));
92
93 if ((tctx->flags & DNS_STYLEFLAG_MULTILINE) != 0)
94 RETERR(str_totext(" )", target));
95
96 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
97}

99static inline isc_result_t
100fromwire_sink(ARGS_FROMWIRE) {
101 isc_region_t sr;
102
103 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_sink);
104
105 UNUSED(type);
106 UNUSED(rdclass);
107 UNUSED(dctx);
108 UNUSED(options);
109
110 isc_buffer_activeregion(source, &sr);
111 if (sr.length < 3)
112 return (ISC_R_UNEXPECTEDEND);
113
114 RETERR(mem_tobuffer(target, sr.base, sr.length));
115 isc_buffer_forward(source, sr.length);
116 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
117}
118
119static inline isc_result_t
120towire_sink(ARGS_TOWIRE) {
121
122 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_sink);
123 REQUIRE(rdata->length >= 3);
124
125 UNUSED(cctx);
126
127 return (mem_tobuffer(target, rdata->data, rdata->length));
128}
129
130static inline int
131compare_sink(ARGS_COMPARE) {
132 isc_region_t r1;
133 isc_region_t r2;
134
135 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == rdata2->type);
136 REQUIRE(rdata1->rdclass == rdata2->rdclass);
137 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == dns_rdatatype_sink);
138 REQUIRE(rdata1->length >= 3);
139 REQUIRE(rdata2->length >= 3);
140
141 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata1, &r1);
142 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata2, &r2);
143 return (isc_region_compare(&r1, &r2));
144}
145
146static inline isc_result_t
147fromstruct_sink(ARGS_FROMSTRUCT) {
148 dns_rdata_sink_t *sink = source;
149
150 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_sink);
151 REQUIRE(source != NULL);
152 REQUIRE(sink->common.rdtype == type);
153 REQUIRE(sink->common.rdclass == rdclass);
154
155 UNUSED(type);
156 UNUSED(rdclass);
157
158 /* Meaning */
159 RETERR(uint8_tobuffer(sink->meaning, target));
160
161 /* Coding */
162 RETERR(uint8_tobuffer(sink->coding, target));
163
164 /* Subcoding */
165 RETERR(uint8_tobuffer(sink->subcoding, target));
166
167 /* Data */
168 return (mem_tobuffer(target, sink->data, sink->datalen));
169}
170
171static inline isc_result_t
172tostruct_sink(ARGS_TOSTRUCT) {
173 dns_rdata_sink_t *sink = target;
174 isc_region_t sr;
175
176 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_sink);
177 REQUIRE(target != NULL);
178 REQUIRE(rdata->length >= 3);
179
180 sink->common.rdclass = rdata->rdclass;
181 sink->common.rdtype = rdata->type;
182 ISC_LINK_INIT(&sink->common, link);
183
184 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &sr);
185
186 /* Meaning */
187 if (sr.length < 1)
188 return (ISC_R_UNEXPECTEDEND);
189 sink->meaning = uint8_fromregion(&sr);
190 isc_region_consume(&sr, 1);
191
192 /* Coding */
193 if (sr.length < 1)
194 return (ISC_R_UNEXPECTEDEND);
195 sink->coding = uint8_fromregion(&sr);
196 isc_region_consume(&sr, 1);
197
198 /* Subcoding */
199 if (sr.length < 1)
200 return (ISC_R_UNEXPECTEDEND);
201 sink->subcoding = uint8_fromregion(&sr);
202 isc_region_consume(&sr, 1);
203
204 /* Data */
205 sink->datalen = sr.length;
206 sink->data = mem_maybedup(mctx, sr.base, sink->datalen);
207 if (sink->data == NULL)
208 return (ISC_R_NOMEMORY);
209
210 sink->mctx = mctx;
211 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
212}
213
214static inline void
215freestruct_sink(ARGS_FREESTRUCT) {
216 dns_rdata_sink_t *sink = (dns_rdata_sink_t *) source;
217
218 REQUIRE(source != NULL);
219 REQUIRE(sink->common.rdtype == dns_rdatatype_sink);
220
221 if (sink->mctx == NULL)
222 return;
223
224 if (sink->data != NULL)
225 isc_mem_free(sink->mctx, sink->data);
226 sink->mctx = NULL;
227}

229static inline isc_result_t
230additionaldata_sink(ARGS_ADDLDATA) {
231 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_sink);
232
233 UNUSED(rdata);
234 UNUSED(add);
235 UNUSED(arg);
236
237 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
238}

240static inline isc_result_t
241digest_sink(ARGS_DIGEST) {
242 isc_region_t r;
243
244 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_sink);
245
246 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &r);
247
248 return ((digest)(arg, &r));
249}
